{"tid":2126632,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屯門康和急增至23人中招  安老院連環爆 恐拖垮公院","createTime":"2020-07-27T03:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T04:06:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"54d60cd97c0ae7d44529693eb73ae7d55e8206a7","tid":2126632,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:11:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200727/LZP2V3JX34YC3ZSEJ7ACKB2DC4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2FLZP2V3JX34YC3ZSEJ7ACKB2DC4%2F&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qx6d04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=7eae70d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2FLZP2V3JX34YC3ZSEJ7ACKB2DC4%2F&h=3d4ac9d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200727/LZP2V3JX34YC3ZSEJ7ACKB2DC4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n屯門康和急增至23人中招 <br />\n安老院連環爆 恐拖垮公院<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎大爆發，社區院舍成為最弱一環。深水埗元州街的敬福安老院有一名院友染疫，同層25名院友及員工須要檢疫，粉嶺的耀能協會華心護康中心亦有一名職員確診。屯門康和護老中心黃金分院更新增八宗確診及13宗初步確診個案，計及初步確診者的群組規模達到23人。醫學會傳染病顧問委員會主席梁子超相信，安老院舍群組將陸續爆發，其規模和嚴重程度可以拖垮醫療系統。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：林鄭硬頸累事 建制也不滿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0J34am_9PFgBGKWpqndjpaW7wjs=/1134x748/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D22OQCBURJLXGDOBPBDHZHM66U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0J34am_9PFgBGKWpqndjpaW7wjs%3D%2F1134x748%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD22OQCBURJLXGDOBPBDHZHM66U.gif&h=8c9bb020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門康和護老中心再有新增確診個案，昨早仍有院友未有撤離。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君昨於疫情簡報會上表示，截至周六，再有三間院舍現確診個案，其中屯門康和護老中心的黃金分院新增八宗確診，包括兩名職員及六名院友，以及。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n敬福25人須檢疫<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：當專家冇到 林鄭豁出大禍  無視警告四個月 議員促向全港道歉<br />\n<br />\n深水埗元州街敬福安老院亦有一名院友感染病毒，由於院舍與其他樓層分隔。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n粉嶺的耀能協會華心護康中心亦有一名職員確診，張竹君表示，有關院舍是。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n本報記者昨到敬福安老院了解，院舍位於華興大廈1樓及2樓，3樓以上為民居。在安老院旁邊店舖工作的楊先生指，昨日下午。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i3xi4CnRpueNH5XZpY_JuXIaDIE=/1049x608/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U5EFSQSH6XB2KY5YIVSRC2I3BI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi3xi4CnRpueNH5XZpY_JuXIaDIE%3D%2F1049x608%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU5EFSQSH6XB2KY5YIVSRC2I3BI.gif&h=e32d1335&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n粉嶺耀能協會華心護康中心員工確診，晚上職員亦穿上全套防護裝備進行清潔。<br />\n<br />\n大廈住戶Q先生（化名）表示，不太擔心會被院友傳染，但居民與安老院友共用一部升降機。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0bw2vY0wPYLBW1i9u-AlCZAHxLE=/730x543/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O4SE4PV4SE3VURXS7P5LKEL5JI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0bw2vY0wPYLBW1i9u-AlCZAHxLE%3D%2F730x543%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO4SE4PV4SE3VURXS7P5LKEL5JI.gif&h=663833e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n康和護老中心外渠口傳出濃烈漂白水味，估計職員清潔後，將污水從渠口排出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁子超︰繼發性爆發比例高<br />\n<br />\n安老院舍相繼有群組爆發，長者堪憂。醫管局至昨日共有908名病人。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n醫學會傳染病顧問委員會主席梁子超表示，社區傳播全面滲透之下，老人家。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。地方隔離⋯⋯最後失救」。<br />\n<br />\n他續說，即使院舍做好防護措施，仍會有院舍群組陸續爆發，希望院舍員工放假時亦不要外出，院舍亦做好分層分組防控。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/y5V4u5NLFzhkaLNdkFlKP97yOeU=/758x564/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4NJ56ARFXWHN5ONEMSTFVU4KPE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fy5V4u5NLFzhkaLNdkFlKP97yOeU%3D%2F758x564%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4NJ56ARFXWHN5ONEMSTFVU4KPE.gif&h=448da03f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n居於康和隔壁的居民劉先生於家門外噴灑漂白水。"},{"pid":"b875104f1f8b832d6fd1a3047686bde3dafc2392","tid":2126632,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:12:40.000Z","msg":"最好向南進發，惹埋何已完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42b5ead843e4e84e9c78161404bc0a2938858b5","tid":2126632,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:13:47.000Z","msg":"國定廢佬剷除期"},{"pid":"315b31aa1164186b84c7f9e0fe008aa9d02686ef","tid":2126632,"uid":9933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:14:49.000Z","msg":"幾好, 爆多D死哂D廢老"},{"pid":"af1084a7ace20125c7d7c5c5b79a73aac7fe7510","tid":2126632,"uid":80243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:16:26.000Z","msg":"。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"7018430645c985fa01c80eceb4ed7a9708673abd","tid":2126632,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:17:43.000Z","msg":"多謝林奠柒婆送禮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55df4e3ee288d105744582c455183e36ffde044","tid":2126632,"uid":155253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:18:26.000Z","msg":"我就住係隔離村屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bc6a759556d69f4a219c51db102a7c4292d2c5","tid":2126632,"uid":10503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:19:29.000Z","msg":"一車車掌心雷冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225beaeb64f3b4e01ae11c0063d3db7c6dc0bc0b","tid":2126632,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:19:45.000Z","msg":"廢佬消滅計劃"},{"pid":"cdc2fd2fc050617ea6210216bc535ae43e64bda2","tid":2126632,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T03:51:33.000Z","msg":"大銼建制票倉<br />\n林奠一定好大壓力<br />\n佢最怕俾建制話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但次次俾建制話完就會記者會到爆響口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7b6bd6106d0cffe98f0500ff0c882a6cf0efcc","tid":2126632,"uid":277235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T04:06:18.000Z","msg":"解決人口老化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />　<br />\n安樂死會唔會人道啲。"}]}